title: MUMBLE_CLEAR_VOICE_TARGET_PLAYERS
content:
0x912E21DA// MumbleClearVoiceTargetPlayers
void MUMBLE_CLEAR_VOICE_TARGET_PLAYERS(int targetId);Parameters:targetId: A Mumble voice target ID, ranging from 1..30 (inclusive).Clears players from the target list for the specified Mumble voice target ID.
